@startuml sequence-overview
!include theme.iuml
title Trilium ETAPI MCP — overview

skinparam responseMessageBelowArrow true
autonumber

actor "MCP client\n(Claude Code, …)" as Client
participant "trilium-mcp\n(this repo)" as Sidecar #98D486
participant "Trilium\nETAPI" as Trilium

Client -> Sidecar : MCP tool call over HTTP\nAuthorization: <ETAPI token>
Sidecar -> Trilium : same token forwarded to /etapi
Trilium --> Sidecar : notes data
Sidecar --> Client : MCP tool result

note over Sidecar : Turns each ETAPI endpoint into an MCP tool.\nHolds no secret — the client's token is the only credential.

@enduml
